name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForChronicPulmonaryDiseases
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Chronic Pulmonary Diseases
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to chronic pulmonary disorders.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes (but not limited to) asthma, COPD, cystic fibrosis, pulmonary sarcoidosis, and obstructive sleep apnea.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
